"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"UTD.htm?23/12/23747?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Uterine cancer (The Basics)",
"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"UTD.htm?11/1/11283?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Ovarian cancer (The Basics)",
"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"UTD.htm?27/61/28626?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Sertoli-Leydig cell tumor (The Basics)",
"      </a>",
"     </p>",
"     <p>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"UTD.htm?6/16/6405?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Abdominal hysterectomy (Beyond the Basics)",
"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"UTD.htm?33/48/34564?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Vaginal hysterectomy (Beyond the Basics)",
"      </a>",
"     </p>",
